Item:
Atribut: id, name, category, price, quantity, description.
Metode: add_item(), remove_item(), update_item(), display_item_info().

Category:
Atribut: id, name, description.
Metode: add_category(), remove_category(), update_category(), display_category_info().

Inventory:
Atribut: items (daftar objek Item), categories (daftar objek Category).
Metode: add_item_to_inventory(), remove_item_from_inventory(), generate_report(),
        track_stock_level(), notify_low_stock().
        
User:
Atribut: id, username, role.
Metode: login(), logout(), authorize_action().

AuditLog:
Atribut: log_entries (daftar perubahan yang dicatat).
Metode: add_log_entry(), display_logs().